{
  "description": "A close-up shot reveals the intricate details of a pink lily's interior. The vibrant pink petals curve and fold, creating a soft, organic backdrop.  The pistil and stamens are the central focus, with the pistil appearing as a delicate, slightly translucent, light green structure topped with a cluster of dark purple or brown speckles. The stamens are thin, pale yellow stalks tipped with a darker, reddish-brown pollen.  The lighting emphasizes the texture of the petals and the pollen, creating a dramatic contrast. The depth of field is shallow, blurring the outer parts of the petals and highlighting the core floral anatomy.",
